      "description": "The Franklin Multisector Income ETF (MULT) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in broad credit fixed income. The fund is actively managed, investing in a diversified portfolio of domestic and international debt securities across multiple fixed income sectors. The fund primarily seeks a high level of current income, and to a lesser extent, long-term capital appreciation. MULT was launched on Aug 26, 2025 and is issued by Franklin Templeton.",
